WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:03.999
Did you try to stall them?

00:04.000 --> 00:05.130
Write to Lorraine,

00:05.140 --> 00:08.090
tell my brother-in-law that these
letters will reach our friends.

00:08.115 --> 00:10.878
And have my courier meet me
at the tavern in Paris.

00:11.608 --> 00:13.356
Go, you idiot. Run.

