00:24.243 --> 00:26.243
You are a heavy sleeper, monsieur.

00:26.253 --> 00:28.546
How dare you wake me
in the middle of the night?

00:28.571 --> 00:30.172
The King wants to see you.

00:41.363 --> 00:43.223
Am I in trouble?

00:43.233 --> 00:46.423
All we know is we must get you
to the palace without delay.

00:47.183 --> 00:49.343
- Why such urgency?
- Pull up your hood.

01:01.963 --> 01:03.565
Come on, Christophe.

01:06.273 --> 01:08.233
Josephine said it would be all right.

01:08.243 --> 01:10.203
My wife has a good heart.

01:10.213 --> 01:13.668
Sylvie and her friends
just need a small place to meet in.

01:13.693 --> 01:15.593
Your friends are trouble.

01:49.183 --> 01:51.242
This man has fallen. He needs help.

01:51.243 --> 01:52.881
Get him a chair.

01:53.353 --> 01:56.611
That's it, man.
It's all right. It's all right.

01:57.393 --> 01:59.353
Oh, now, easy, easy.

02:03.213 --> 02:05.618
Would that Musketeer
be one of your friends?

02:06.419 --> 02:08.549
Easy does it. Right, that's okay.

02:09.758 --> 02:11.828
- Away from me.
- Have some wine.

02:11.853 --> 02:13.760
Have some wine.

02:24.343 --> 02:25.836
I've been robbed!

02:27.077 --> 02:28.077
Hey!

02:29.223 --> 02:30.352
Come here!

02:30.353 --> 02:31.383
Stop! Stop!

02:41.408 --> 02:42.578
You cannot kill me.

02:42.798 --> 02:44.518
I'm the Duke of Orleans.

02:44.598 --> 02:46.064
The King's brother.

03:17.131 --> 03:19.831
